# es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The cumulative option allows you to see how your data accumulates over different\n"
"                values. When enabled, the histogram bars represent the running total of frequencies\n"
"                up to each bin. This helps you understand how likely it is to encounter values\n"
"                below a certain point. Keep in mind that enabling cumulative doesn't change your\n"
"                original data, it just changes the way the histogram is displayed."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Opcija kumulativno vam omogućava da vidite kako se vaši podaci akumuliraju pri različitim\n"
"                vrednostima. Kada je omogućena, trake histograma predstavljaju tekući zbir učestanosti\n"
"                do svakog bina. Ovo vam pomaže da razumete koliko je verovatno da naiđete na vrednosti\n"
"                ispod određene tačke. Imajte na umu da omogućavanje kumulativnog ne menja vaše\n"
"                izvorne podatke, samo menja način na koji se histogram prikazuje."

# es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The normalize option transforms the histogram values into proportions or\n"
"                probabilities by dividing each bin's count by the total count of data points.\n"
"                This normalization process ensures that the resulting values sum up to 1,\n"
"                enabling a relative comparison of the data's distribution and providing a\n"
"                clearer understanding of the proportion of data points within each bin."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                Opcija normalizacije pretvara vrednosti histograma u proporcije ili\n"
"                verovatnoće deljenjem broja u svakom binu ukupnim brojem tačaka podataka.\n"
"                Ovaj proces normalizacije osigurava da zbir dobijenih vrednosti bude 1,\n"
"                što omogućava relativno poređenje raspodele podataka i pruža\n"
"                jasniju predstavu o udelu tačaka podataka u svakom binu."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
