# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid ""
"Filters with the same group key will be ORed together within the group, "
"while different filter groups will be ANDed together. Undefined group keys "
"are treated as unique groups, i.e. are not grouped together. For example, if"
" a table has three filters, of which two are for departments Finance and "
"Marketing (group key = 'department'), and one refers to the region Europe "
"(group key = 'region'), the filter clause would apply the filter (department"
" = 'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND (region = 'Europe')."
msgstr ""
"Filteri sa istim ključem grupe biće povezani sa ILI unutar grupe, dok će "
"različite grupe filtera biti povezane sa I. Nedefinisani ključevi grupe se "
"tretiraju kao jedinstvene grupe, tj. ne grupišu se zajedno. Na primer, ako "
"tabela ima tri filtera, od kojih su dva za odeljenja Finansije i Marketing "
"(ključ grupe = 'department'), a jedan se odnosi na region Evropa (ključ "
"grupe = 'region'), klauza filtera bi primenila filter (department = "
"'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND (region = 'Europe')."

