msgid ""
"SQL Lab uses your browser's local storage to store queries and results.\n"
"Currently, you are using %(currentUsage)s KB out of %(maxStorage)d KB storage space.\n"
"To keep SQL Lab from crashing, please delete some query tabs.\n"
"You can re-access these queries by using the Save feature before you delete the tab.\n"
"Note that you will need to close other SQL Lab windows before you do this."
msgstr ""
"SQL Lab koristi lokalnu memoriju vašeg pregledača za čuvanje upita i rezultata.\n"
"Trenutno koristite %(currentUsage)s KB od ukupno %(maxStorage)d KB prostora za skladištenje.\n"
"Da biste sprečili da SQL Lab prekine rad, obrišite neke kartice sa upitima.\n"
"Možete ponovo pristupiti ovim upitima korišćenjem funkcije Sačuvaj pre nego što obrišete karticu.\n"
"Imajte na umu da ćete morati da zatvorite druge prozore SQL Lab-a pre nego što to učinite."

