"The description can be displayed as widget headers in the dashboard view. "
"Supports markdown."
msgstr ""
"Opis se može prikazati kao zaglavlje vidžeta u prikazu kontrolne table. "
"Podržava markdown."

# uk]
msgid "The display name of your dashboard"
msgstr "Prikazani naziv vaše kontrolne table"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The distance between cells, in pixels"
msgstr "Razmak između ćelija, u pikselima"

# de, es, fa, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid ""
"The duration of time in seconds before the cache is invalidated. Set to -1 "
"to bypass the cache."
msgstr ""
"Vreme u sekundama pre nego što keš postane nevažeći. Postavite na -1 da "
"biste zaobišli keš."

# de, es, fa, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid "The encoding format of the lines"
msgstr "Format kodiranja linija"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
