"The engine_params object gets unpacked into the sqlalchemy.create_engine "
"call."
msgstr "Objekat engine_params se raspakuje u pozivu sqlalchemy.create_engine."

# fr, ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The exponent to compute all sizes from. \"EXP\" only"
msgstr "Eksponent na osnovu kojeg se izračunavaju sve veličine. Samo za „EXP”"

# uk]
#, python-format
msgid "The extension %(id)s could not be loaded."
msgstr "Ekstenzija %(id)s nije mogla biti učitana."

# fr, ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid ""
"The extent of the map on application start. FIT DATA automatically sets the "
"extent so that all data points are included in the viewport. CUSTOM allows "
"users to define the extent manually."
msgstr ""
"Obim mape pri pokretanju aplikacije. FIT DATA automatski podešava obim tako "
"da svi podaci budu uključeni u prikaz. CUSTOM omogućava korisnicima da ručno"
" definišu obim."

# ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The feature property to use for point labels"
msgstr "Svojstvo entiteta koje se koristi za oznake tačaka"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following entries in `series_columns` are missing in `columns`: "
"%(columns)s. "
msgstr "Sledeći unosi u `series_columns` nedostaju u `columns`: %(columns)s. "

msgid ""
"The following fields contain sensitive information that was masked during "
"export. Please provide the values to import this database."
msgstr ""
"Sledeća polja sadrže osetljive informacije koje su maskirane prilikom "
"izvoza. Unesite vrednosti da biste uvezli ovu bazu podataka."

# es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk]
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following filters have the 'Select first filter value by default'\n"
"                    option checked and could not be loaded, which is preventing the dashboard\n"
"                    from rendering: %s"
msgstr ""
"Sledeći filteri imaju označenu opciju 'Izaberi podrazumevano prvu vrednost filtera'\n"
"                    i nije ih moguće učitati, što sprečava prikazivanje\n"
"                    kontrolne table: %s"

# uk]
msgid "The font size of the point labels"
msgstr "Veličina fonta oznaka tačaka"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid "The function to use when aggregating points into groups"
msgstr "Funkcija koja se koristi pri agregiranju tačaka u grupe"

# uk]
msgid "The group has been created successfully."
msgstr "Grupa je uspešno kreirana."

# lv, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The group has been updated successfully."
msgstr "Grupa je uspešno ažurirana."

# fr, ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The height of the current zoom level to compute all heights from"
msgstr ""
"Visina trenutnog nivoa zumiranja na osnovu koje se izračunavaju sve visine"

# es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid ""
"The histogram chart displays the distribution of a dataset by\n"
"          representing the frequency or count of values within different ranges or bins.\n"
"          It helps visualize patterns, clusters, and outliers in the data and provides\n"
"          insights into its shape, central tendency, and spread."
msgstr ""
"Histogram grafikon prikazuje distribuciju skupa podataka\n"
"          predstavljajući frekvenciju ili broj vrednosti u različitim opsezima ili binovima.\n"
"          Pomaže u vizualizaciji obrazaca, klastera i odstupanja u podacima i pruža\n"
"          uvid u njegov oblik, centralnu tendenciju i raspršenost."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid "The host \"%(hostname)s\" might be down and can't be reached."
msgstr "Host „%(hostname)s” možda ne radi i nije dostupan."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The host \"%(hostname)s\" might be down, and can't be reached on port "
"%(port)s."
msgstr "Host „%(hostname)s” možda ne radi i nije dostupan na portu %(port)s."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The host might be down, and can't be reached on the provided port."
msgstr "Host možda ne radi i nije dostupan na navedenom portu."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid "The hostname \"%(hostname)s\" cannot be resolved."
msgstr "Naziv hosta „%(hostname)s” se ne može razrešiti."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The hostname provided can't be resolved."
msgstr "Navedeni naziv hosta se ne može razrešiti."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The id of the active chart"
msgstr "ID aktivnog grafikona"

# ru, sk, uk]
msgid ""
"The image URL of the icon to display for GeoJSON points. Note that the image"
" URL must conform to the content security policy (CSP) in order to load "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"URL slike ikone koja se prikazuje za GeoJSON tačke. Imajte na umu da URL "
"slike mora biti u skladu sa politikom bezbednosti sadržaja (CSP) da bi se "
"pravilno učitala."

# ru, sk, uk]
msgid ""
"The initial level (depth) of the tree. If set as -1 all nodes are expanded."
msgstr ""
"Početni nivo (dubina) stabla. Ako je postavljeno na -1, svi čvorovi su "
"prošireni."

# ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The layer attribution"
msgstr "Atribucija sloja"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid "The lower limit of the threshold range of the Isoband"
msgstr "Donja granica praga opsega izoband-a"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid ""
"The maximum number of subdivisions of each group; lower values are pruned "
"first"
msgstr "Maksimalan broj podela svake grupe; niže vrednosti se prve uklanjaju"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The maximum value of metrics. It is an optional configuration"
msgstr "Maksimalna vrednost metrika. To je opcionalna konfiguracija"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The metadata_params in Extra field is not configured correctly. The key "
"%(key)s is invalid."
msgstr ""
"Parametar metadata_params u polju Extra nije pravilno konfigurisan. Ključ "
"%(key)s je nevažeći."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The metadata_params in Extra field is not configured correctly. The key "
"%{key}s is invalid."
msgstr ""
"Parametar metadata_params u polju Extra nije pravilno konfigurisan. Ključ "
"%{key}s je nevažeći."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid ""
"The metadata_params object gets unpacked into the sqlalchemy.MetaData call."
msgstr "Objekat metadata_params se raspakuje u poziv sqlalchemy.MetaData."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid ""
"The minimum number of rolling periods required to show a value. For instance"
" if you do a cumulative sum on 7 days you may want your \"Min Period\" to be"
" 7, so that all data points shown are the total of 7 periods. This will hide"
" the \"ramp up\" taking place over the first 7 periods"
msgstr ""
"Minimalan broj rolnih perioda potrebnih da bi se prikazala vrednost. Na "
"primer, ako radite kumulativni zbir za 7 dana, možda ćete želeti da vaš "
"\"Min period\" bude 7, tako da sve prikazane tačke podataka predstavljaju "
"zbir od 7 perioda. Ovo će sakriti \"naglo povećanje\" koje se javlja tokom "
"prvih 7 perioda"

# ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid ""
"The minimum value of metrics. It is an optional configuration. If not set, "
"it will be the minimum value of the data"
msgstr ""
"Minimalna vrednost metrika. To je opcionalna konfiguracija. Ako nije "
"podešeno, biće minimalna vrednost podataka"

# ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The name of the geometry column"
msgstr "Naziv kolone geometrije"

# fr, ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, uk]
msgid "The name of the layer as described in GetCapabilities"
msgstr "Naziv sloja kao što je opisano u GetCapabilities"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid "The name of the rule must be unique"
msgstr "Naziv pravila mora biti jedinstven"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid "The number color \"steps\""
msgstr "Broj \"koraka\" boje"

# es, fa, ja, lv, mi, ru, sk, sl, uk]
msgid "The number of bins for the histogram"
msgstr "Broj binova za histogram"

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
msgid ""
"The number of hours, negative or positive, to shift the time column. This "
"can be used to move UTC time to local time."
msgstr ""
"Broj sati, negativan ili pozitivan, za pomeranje kolone vremena. Ovo se može"
" koristiti za pomeranje UTC vremena u lokalno vreme."

# uk]
#, python-format
msgid "The number of results displayed is limited to %(rows)d."
msgstr "Broj prikazanih rezultata je ograničen na %(rows)d."

# de, es, fa, ja, lv, mi, nl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk]
#, python-format
msgid "The number of rows displayed is limited to %(rows)d by the dropdown."
msgstr "Broj prikazanih redova je ograničen na %(rows)d padajućim menijem."

# de, es, fa, fr, ja, lv, mi, nl, pl, pt_BR, ru, sk, sl, uk, zh, zh_TW]
#, python-format
msgid ""
